#VenmoQRCActivationDetailBody:
Accept Venmo payments for your business and remove the need for customers to touch your phone or card reader.

Ask your customer to open their camera or Venmo app, then present your QR code and scan. Once your customer taps 'confirm', the payment is complete! By using Venmo, you'll get your money instantly. The fee will differ from your regular card rates.

Learn more about the payment method and pricing here.
